e":"2016-12-13T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝個「拆樓神器」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低音炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錄低佢地把聲再播番畀佢地聽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講佢地係住我上面唔知邊層 唔想炸錯好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9389d59ed31e7d477615b94279a5b6cba93f2be6","tid":37151,"uid":21104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隔離屋都有兩公婆成日鬧交，嚴格嚟講應該係畀老婆鬧，剩係聽過個男死狗咁嘅聲，仲要一個月起碼一次，每次12點後先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌尤其依家考final 嘈撚到我想燒powerpoint<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd3c1e75c38e31c036add8600a1ac9264b7c056","tid":37151,"uid":61788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"依家仲有冇嘈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}